# Analysis — Revision 2026

R scripts for the revised analysis submitted to *Epidemics* in June 2026.

## Contents

- `01_fit_saturated_model.R` — Saturated NP model fit (quintile-specific λ_pre and λ_omi)
- `02_fit_parsimonious_model.R` — Parsimonious model fit (shared Omicron multiplier)
- `03_compare_models.R` — AIC, BIC, likelihood ratio test
- `04_calculate_irr_with_ci.R` — IRRs with delta-method CIs
- `05_calculate_omicron_multipliers_and_rho.R` — Omicron multipliers and ρ with CIs (saturated model)
- `06_calculate_parsimonious_rho_ci.R` — Parsimonious-model ρ CI (added in revision)
- `07_generate_sample_size_table_S1B.R` — Generates Supplementary Table S1B (sample sizes by quintile and pandemic period)

All scripts expect to be run from the repository root and read data from `Data/cbs_seroprev_by_quintile.csv`.

## Outputs

- Model fit objects: `saturated_model_estimate_rho.rds`, `parsimonious_model_estimate_rho.rds`
- Inference objects: `irr_estimates_with_ci.rds`, `omicron_multipliers_with_ci.rds`
- Supplementary tables: `Table_S1B_sample_sizes.csv`

Figure-generating scripts live in `Figures/revision_2026/`.
